  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Kdeadmin</title>

    <para>This package provides several administration tools for <application>KDE4
    </application>. These include a tool for managing users, a cron command schedule editor,
    a printer administration tool and a log file viewer.</para>

    &lfs70_checked;

